Addressing a media briefing on Monday morning the mayor also pleaded with the media to respect the processes as they unfold. I am sure you will appreciate the fact that this is an involved process which requires all those interested in stability to be sober-minded. For this reason we wish to appeal to the media houses not to exert unnecessary pressure on this process by coming up with sensational scoops he said.After agreeing to a political coalition which allowed the ruling ANC to retain some municipalities following the local government elections the African Independent Congress as part of a bargaining deal demanded the reincorporation of Matatiele in KZN in return for it helping out the ANC.TMG Digital/DispatchLIVE